snippet.title: Collectors Cove Announcement Trailer
snippet.description: EXCLUSIVE REVEAL: Set sail on a cozy farming adventure with your animal companion in Collector's Cove! Explore diverse regions and discover rare crops and fish. Enjoy the peace and quiet while completing your Collector's compendium and rise to the rank of a Named Collector. https://store.steampowered.com/app/2867470/Collectors_Cove/ #indiegames #cozygames #gaming
